8. Cyber-Physical Governance

QUENNE continuously decides:
   •   where compute runs
   •   how much power is used
   •   how systems cool
   •   how threats are blocked

This is real-time infrastructure governance.

⸻

9. Security & Resilience

QUENNE integrates:
   •   anomaly detection
   •   cyber-physical intrusion detection
   •   self-healing control loops
   •   multi-agent fault tolerance

It is designed for hostile environments.

